# 🌦️ Weather App with 3D Animations

A **responsive** and **interactive** Weather App that fetches real-time weather data using the OpenWeather API. The app features **cool 3D animations** and dynamic backgrounds based on weather conditions. 🌎✨  

![Weather App Demo](https://your-image-url.com) <!-- Replace with actual demo screenshot -->

---

## 🚀 Features
✅ **Live Weather Updates** - Get real-time weather data for any city.  
✅ **3D Animations** - Cool animations for different weather conditions.  
✅ **Dynamic Backgrounds** - The UI adapts based on weather (rain, snow, sunny, etc.).  
✅ **Responsive Design** - Works on **mobile, tablet, and desktop**.  
✅ **Search Functionality** - Users can check weather for any location.  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **HTML, CSS, JavaScript** (Frontend)
- **OpenWeather API** (Weather Data)
- **GSAP / CSS Animations** (Smooth animations)

---

